<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">產業描述：</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 36pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">橡膠製品製造業</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">員　　工：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">95</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">人</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">資</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">本</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">額：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">1000</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">萬元</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">聯</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">絡</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">人：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">郭小姐</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司地址：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">台中市大甲區東三街</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">8</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">號</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><a href="http://www.104.com.tw/jobbank/custjob/index.php?r=cust&amp;j=386042263846402556583a1d1d1d1d5f24437323189j56"><span style="padding: 0cm; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: #003399; font-family: '新細明體','serif';">地圖</span></a></span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">電話：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt;"><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">04-26820688</span></span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">分機</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">215</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">傳真：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">04-26821156</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; margin-left: 35.45pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司網址：</span><a href="http://www.zon.com.tw/">http://www.zon.com.tw/</a></span></p>
<h2 style="margin: 16.35pt 0cm 0pt 2.75pt; line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;<strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司簡介</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="margin: 0cm 6.55pt 0pt 10.9pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">本公司成立於</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">1985</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">年，主要從事橡膠零件設計及各種工業用橡膠產品製造，擁有為數不少的客戶群，市場分佈於國內與海外。</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><br /></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">我們擁有優秀的經營團隊，整體的營運穩定，獲利狀況也逐年提升。</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><br /></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">～歡迎優秀的您一起加入～</span></span></p>
<h2 style="margin: 16.35pt 0cm 0pt 2.75pt; line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;<strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">主要商品／服務項目</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="margin: 0cm 6.55pt 0pt 10.9pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">橡膠零件設計及專業製造，含</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">O</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">環、墊片、襯套、減震橡膠、防塵套及所有密封件</span></span></p>
<h2 style="margin: 16.35pt 0cm 0pt 2.75pt; line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;<strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">福利制度</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="margin: 0cm 6.55pt 0pt 10.9pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">1</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、勞保</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">/</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">健保</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">/</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">團保</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><br /><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">2</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、三節獎金</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">/</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">禮券</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><br /><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">3</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、定期健康檢查</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><br /><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">4</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、年度國內、外旅遊</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">/</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">聚餐</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><br /><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">5</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">、生日蛋糕</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"><br /><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; background-color: #ffffff;">6</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; background-color: #ffffff;">、分紅獎金</span></span></p>
